episodes.title: Your Will Shall Decide Your Destiny
episodes.plot: Anne arrives at Green Gables and struggles with fitting into her new environment.

episodes.title: I Am No Bird, and No Net Ensnares Me
episodes.plot: Filled with worry Matthew Cuthbert races to find Anne before it's too late.

episodes.title: But What Is So Headstrong as Youth?
episodes.plot: Anne is introduced to the inner social workings of public school, while Marilla is introduced to the inner social workings of Avonlea's progressive young mothers.

episodes.title: An Inward Treasure Born
episodes.plot: Anne and Marilla struggle with Anne's staunch boycott of the local school. A minister's backward advice has a reverse effect, causing Anne to fiercely challenge gender norms.

episodes.title: Tightly Knotted to a Similar String
episodes.plot: Anne is allowed to ask her best friend Diana over for afternoon tea, things start to go wrong when she looks for the Raspberry Cordial.

episodes.title: Remorse Is the Poison of Life
episodes.plot: An emergency occurs in Diana's family while her Mom is away.

episodes.title: Wherever You Are Is My Home
episodes.plot: The Cuthberts vow to do whatever it takes to save the farm, which reminds Anne of the strength of friendship and love.
